Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:35.12,lassie default,Sam Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:391078,395124}Hey, someone tell Brad Hamilton!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:36.87,lassie default,Sam Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:395124,396876}The baby's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:38.83,lassie default,Sam Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:396876,398836}It's a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:40.21,lassie default,Sam Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:398836,400212}It's a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:50.13,lassie default,Worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:407762,410139}Congrats!\NYou're a father now, you rascal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:53.60,lassie default,Worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:411682,413601}Congratulations!
