Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:02.71,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:480876,482712}Mom, I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:07.80,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:486340,487800}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:13.59,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:490636,493597}Mom, are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:20.10,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:498185,500104}Maybe she's sleeping upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:27.52,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:505860,507528}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:41.91,lassie default,Hamilton,0,0,0,,{TIME:520207,521917}Oh, it's you, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:45.25,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:522376,525254}Did Mrs. Hamilton deliver the baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:46.63,lassie default,Hamilton,0,0,0,,{TIME:525254,526630}Yes, she did!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:51.09,lassie default,Hamilton,0,0,0,,{TIME:526630,531093}Your dad told me that I can take a day off,\Nso I came here right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:53.59,lassie default,Hamilton,0,0,0,,{TIME:531093,533596}The ladies who helped\Nhave all left, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.59,0:08:57.05,lassie default,Hamilton,0,0,0,,{TIME:533596,537058}Come with me.\NYou have to see our child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:58.47,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:537058,538476}Sure, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:00.77,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:538476,540770}Do you know where's my mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:05.27,lassie default,Hamilton,0,0,0,,{TIME:540770,545274}Ah, she left with Dr. Hopper.\NDon't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:07.10,lassie default,Hamilton,0,0,0,,{TIME:545274,547109}Here, this way.\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:12.11,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:549737,552114}Oh, it's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:16.11,lassie default,Hamilton,0,0,0,,{TIME:552531,556118}I know, right? Her eyelashes\Nare so long, she's a true beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:17.11,lassie default,Mrs. Hamilton,0,0,0,,{TIME:556118,557119}John?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:21.20,lassie default,Mrs. Hamilton,0,0,0,,{TIME:557661,561207}I am so grateful\Nto your mother and father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:22.12,lassie default,Mrs. Hamilton,0,0,0,,{TIME:561207,562124}Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:23.95,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:562833,563959}No problem…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:34.55,lassie default,Melissa Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:573052,574553}Ah, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:36.05,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:574804,576055}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:37.55,lassie default,Melissa Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:576055,577556}You're such a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:41.64,lassie default,Melissa Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:578224,581644}I'm sorry,\Nbut I have to go out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:44.52,lassie default,Melissa Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:581644,584522}A patient with peritonitis\Nnow has a cold on top of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:47.56,lassie default,Melissa Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:584522,587566}He is going to have a procedure\Nand I'll have to take care of him tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:50.94,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:588192,590945}But, Mom,\Nyou didn't sleep last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:54.24,lassie default,Melissa Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:592404,594240}Your mother is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:56.57,lassie default,Melissa Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:594240,596575}But will you be able\Nto eat dinner by yourself, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:00.78,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:598452,600788}I'll be fine. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:03.08,lassie default,Melissa Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:600788,603082}All right. You're such a big boy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.66,0:10:08.46,lassie default,Melissa Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:604667,608462}I have prepared the food in a pot,\Nso you only need to heat it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:09.92,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:608462,609922}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:27.48,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:625938,627481}Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:29.77,lassie default,Colin,0,0,0,,{TIME:628732,629775}John?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:31.36,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:629775,631360}Hey, Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.98,lassie default,Colin,0,0,0,,{TIME:631360,633988}I told you before,\NI can't play today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:36.69,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:633988,636699}I know. Did they\Nput you on delivery?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:38.11,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:636699,638117}Are these the goods?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:39.49,lassie default,Colin,0,0,0,,{TIME:638117,639493}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:41.49,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:639493,641495}Looks kinda heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:43.49,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:642246,643497}Hey, how about I help you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:45.79,lassie default,Colin,0,0,0,,{TIME:644123,645791}Oh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:51.00,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:645791,651005}You bet! We can ride together\Nall around the town that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:56.26,lassie default,Colin,0,0,0,,{TIME:652089,656260}Okay. If you ride the bike,\NI'll take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:11:02.09,lassie default,Colin,0,0,0,,{TIME:657678,662099}I was asked to deliver this stuff to places\Nall over the town and to a nearby village.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:04.51,lassie default,Colin,0,0,0,,{TIME:662099,664518}I was wondering\Nhow I'm going to handle that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:09.48,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:665436,669481}Eh, I thought we're gonna\Ndo the deliveries together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:11.90,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:669481,671901}I'm alone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:14.52,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:672943,674528}Well, that's too bad.
Comment: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:23.45,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:683454,683454}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:32.58,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:690461,692588}Oh, it's an airplane!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:41.26,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:696508,701263}Amazing… I'd love\Nto fly one some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:47.77,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:706018,707770}It's landing here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:11.50,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:729500,731502}So awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.47,0:12:32.18,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:748477,752189}Hey, stay away from the bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:36.77,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:752189,756777}Hey, don't do that!\NIt's not mine, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:40.15,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:756777,760155}Don't touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:45.66,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:764451,765661}Aw, this is bad…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:49.83,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:767037,769832}How long are they going\Nto be like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:12:59.92,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:778299,779925}Hey, it's a…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:01.84,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:779925,781844}What is it doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:04.34,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:781844,784346}Whose dog is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:08.18,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:785597,788183}Don't move.\NYou'll be crushed if you move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:13.93,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:792855,793939}Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:28.16,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:805701,808162}Hey, stay where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:32.08,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:810205,812082}Where did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:39.13,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:816545,819131}Hey, where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:43.51,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:822301,823510}Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:47.18,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:824553,827181}Come on, come here…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:53.52,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:829850,833520}Alright. All's good now.\NAre you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:04.15,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:841528,844156}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:05.94,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:844156,845949}Did you get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:32.30,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:867679,872309}Don't go near sheep again.\NYou'll be crushed if you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:34.81,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:872309,874812}Now, go home\Nto your owner. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:41.06,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:876814,881068}I have to deliver these\Nas soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:42.61,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:881068,882611}Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:27.28,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:924778,927281}Oh, I'm so beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:31.07,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:928449,931076}When I go back home,\Nit's dinner all alone…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:38.16,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:935289,938167}What's the matter, buddy?\NYou're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:41.00,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:939668,941003}Could it be…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:44.00,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:942212,944006}That you don't have\Na home to go back to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:49.09,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:947092,949094}Are you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:55.26,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:951680,955267}You look so sad.\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:16:00.02,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:957603,960022}Don't tell me you're sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:05.61,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:962566,965611}This is bad! This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:08.48,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:965611,968489}You just rest.\NI'll take you home immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:18.49,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:974161,978499}Colin! I'm done with the delivery!\NI left the bike outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:19.75,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:978499,979750}Laters!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:23.71,lassie default,Colin,0,0,0,,{TIME:983045,983712}John?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:28.71,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:986507,988717}Faster! Faster! Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:42.27,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:999937,1002272}Look, I lit the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:44.31,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002272,1004316}Now, let's get you warmed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:54.24,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008070,1014243}My mom comes back late pretty often,\Nso I know how to light it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:56.49,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014243,1016495}What do you think?\NFeel any better?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:06.29,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022876,1026296}What a good smell!\NIt's the food Mom has made.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:11.05,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027714,1031051}Let me guess, you're hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:13.88,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032427,1033887}Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:19.51,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037266,1039518}Oh? We ran out of milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:21.43,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039518,1041436}Wait for me.\NI'm going to fetch some!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.86,0:17:34.57,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052864,1054575}Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:46.29,lassie default,Sandy,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063417,1066295}What color is the puppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:48.67,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066295,1068672}Hm, how to describe it…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:53.09,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068672,1073093}It's mostly brown,\Nbut it has also white spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:54.67,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073093,1074678}It's about this big.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:55.88,lassie default,Sandy,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074678,1075887}So it's still just a pup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:01.43,lassie default,Sandy,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078515,1081435}Let me see it next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:02.72,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081435,1082728}Yeah. Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:04.22,lassie default,Sandy,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082728,1084229}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:06.35,lassie default,Sandy,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084646,1086356}It's a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:08.10,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086356,1088108}Thanks for the milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:23.79,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100704,1103790}Here, I brought you some milk.\NIt's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:29.25,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1106209,1109254}What's the matter?\NWeren't you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:38.93,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115218,1118930}What's the matter?\NYou can't drink milk by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:41.39,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119765,1121391}You're like a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:46.43,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122184,1126438}Boy, I am tired.\NIt'd be nice if Dad came home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:58.57,lassie default,Sam Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136657,1138575}Looks like I'm stuck here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:02.62,lassie default,Sam Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139910,1142621}Two people from section 2\Nhaven't returned yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:04.08,lassie default,Sam Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142621,1144081}I wonder what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:09.08,lassie default,Sam Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146375,1149086}They should've come back\Na long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:13.59,lassie default,Sam Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151088,1153590}I hope there wasn't an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:16.63,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155342,1156635}I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:19.59,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156635,1159596}It was a helpless puppy\Njust a few seconds ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:23.72,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160681,1163725}I know. I know!\NThat's what it's after.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.72,0:19:24.89,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163725,1164893}Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:27.68,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166186,1167688}Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:31.65,lassie default,Colin,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169773,1171650}John? Is it you, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.65,0:19:32.69,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171650,1172693}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:37.32,lassie default,Colin,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173735,1177322}Sorry, John.\NI got scolded by Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:40.40,lassie default,Colin,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177322,1180409}He asked if I thanked you\Nfor helping with the delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:42.86,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180409,1182869}Well, how could you?\NI was in such a rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.86,0:19:45.33,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182869,1185330}Say, do you happen\Nto have a baby bottle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:46.28,lassie default,Colin,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185330,1186289}A baby bottle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:51.12,lassie default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1189334,1191128}– A puppy?\N– Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:54.88,lassie default,Colin,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191128,1194881}We just sold the last one\Nto Mrs. Hamilton.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:55.79,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194881,1195799}I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:20:00.88,lassie default,Colin,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196633,1200887}Ah, wait, we still have one.\NIt's the one we used for my little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:04.39,lassie default,Colin,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202556,1204391}Next time, you must\Nshow me that puppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:05.47,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204391,1205475}Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.18,0:20:12.60,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210188,1212607}Can it drink through it, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:22.65,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219656,1222659}You must've been starving.
